  "keyFeatures": [
    "MicroVM isolation with Firecracker or Cloud Hypervisor per workload",
    "Zero-config app deployment from Git repositories through a builder, scheduler, and agent pipeline",
    "Dynamic ingress routing with automatic TLS via a Pingora-based router",
    "PostgreSQL databases provisioned through Neon and running in Cloud Hypervisor-backed microVMs",
    "WireGuard mesh networking and internal DNS for platform service discovery",
    "eBPF data plane for host-side network handling and metrics",
    "SvelteKit dashboard and Rust CLI for day-to-day operations",
    "Dynatrace-backed OpenTelemetry observability across all services",
    "Dagger-backed local CI/CD pipeline with layered validation profiles",
    "Persistent volume support with Ceph-backed RBD snapshots"
  ],
